    "4eb75113-401d-44ee-b1f8-0e8a9d432f24": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "template--19575487660306__4eb75113-401d-44ee-b1f8-0e8a9d432f24-16877746580fb4404c-1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Quick Mop Floor Wipes",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text_color": "",
            "gradient": ""
          }
        },
        "template--19575487660306__4eb75113-401d-44ee-b1f8-0e8a9d432f24-16877746580fb4404c-0": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": ""
          }
        },
        "template--19575487660306__4eb75113-401d-44ee-b1f8-0e8a9d432f24-16877746580fb4404c-2": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Revive your home with the newest cleaning innovation to hit the floors in Australia.</p><p>Our Floor Wipes are uniquely designed wet wipes that come in an extra large size to maximise your time for a better, faster clean.</p><p>It has never been easier to get that super fresh feeling without the fuss. With a range of fragrances, our wet wipes work on tiles, concrete, stone and protect timber and wooden floors without the bucket, mop and water. </p><p>Unlike other floor cleaning wipes, ours are fit to use with any existing broom / floor squeegee / mop you have at home and are disposable, giving you a quick and convenient way to clean more while using less effort.</p><p>Simply wipe, dispose and enjoy a cleaner home — without spreading dirt and germs with reusable cleaning tools. A smarter everyday cleaning solution designed to keep your floors looking fresh, clean and spotless.</p><p></p><p></p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "template--19575487660306__4eb75113-401d-44ee-b1f8-0e8a9d432f24-16877746580fb4404c-1",
