    "b9b043b0-6f7d-46c8-af7e-abe869a1461a": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "6da2bca1-7bd4-441a-aa3b-7bdea2f6e4aa": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-star",
            "icon_width": 76,
            "icon_background_type": "none",
            "icon_background": "",
            "icon_color": "#7f48b0"
          }
        },
        "20603c75-742b-4aa3-9bf1-45b12bc6e953": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Easy to Use",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text_color": "#7f48b0",
            "gradient": ""
          }
        },
        "ed5b4685-7bdc-4d20-9a20-0c3f90df0849": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Cleaning in a flash was never easier. No more stress when there’s a surprise guest, quickly clean after meals, playtime and muddy paws. When all you have to do is pull out a supersize floor wipe and slide it over the top of any broom / floor squeegee / mop at home, it’s a breeze to maintain your floors for more clean in less time.</p>"
          }
        },
        "44b5f786-639e-4c42-94ad-1319a0c6d566": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-happy",
            "icon_width": 84,
            "icon_background_type": "none",
            "icon_background": "",
            "icon_color": "#f7d033"
          }
        },
        "template--19575487660306__b9b043b0-6f7d-46c8-af7e-abe869a1461a-16877746580fb4404c-1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "More Hygenic",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text_color": "#f7d033",
            "gradient": ""
          }
        },
        "template--19575487660306__b9b043b0-6f7d-46c8-af7e-abe869a1461a-16877746580fb4404c-2": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fresh Home Floor Wipes have an antibacterial quality, the simple way to disinfect your floors and home from dirt. No more spreading bacteria from dirty mop heads across your floors, our disposable wipes make it easy to wipe on, dirt off and dispose.</p>"
          }
        },
        "3c1ba536-b759-485a-a1d6-4a0e2285b3b1": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-leaf",
            "icon_width": 84,
            "icon_background_type": "none",
            "icon_background": "",
            "icon_color": "#4888b0"
          }
        },
        "93aab34e-8df3-4da3-bd0e-5957aca7930e": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Fresh Scent",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text_color": "#4888b0",
            "gradient": ""
          }
        },
        "5a0ca4b1-3ba2-4244-bb5c-8d4898861195": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Our wipes come in a range of fresh scents that you can’t get from the average mop and water. Most wipes are smaller and unscented, leaving a chemical smell and far less shine. When you use our floor wipes, you’ll feel the sparkling wet shine and fresh scents of lavender and luxury boutique hotels, that give you the look and smell of a superior deep clean.</p>"
          }
        },
        "bcae4e72-3928-4c2c-a157-3faf38d62f0c": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-love",
            "icon_width": 84,
            "icon_background_type": "none",
            "icon_background": "#fb33a6",
            "icon_color": "#7f48b0"
          }
        },
        "9eb88661-770b-4d1a-8df2-31cfdc83f9a2": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Daily Routine",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text_color": "#7f48b0",
            "gradient": ""
          }
        },
        "0e61e33d-d7df-49ef-889f-02e604013471": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Households across Australia can’t get enough of our Fresh Home Floor Wipes. You’ll get addicted to the scent and the shine from one quick and easy swipe. Cleaning made so simple you’ll want to wipe your floors on the daily.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
